# 🌐 Web Development Assignment – HTML, CSS & JavaScript

## 📁 Project Overview
This folder contains a series of web development assignments focused on building responsive and interactive web pages using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**. Each task demonstrates core front-end development concepts, including semantic markup, styling techniques, and dynamic behavior.

## 🧠 Objectives
- Practice semantic HTML structure
- Apply responsive design principles using CSS
- Implement interactivity with JavaScript
- Strengthen modular coding habits and documentation

